In [58]:
df_top200 = df.head(200)
df_top200
def vasha_funkcia(url):
    page = requests.get(url)
    soup = BeautifulSoup(page.text, "html.parser")
    height = soup.find_all("span", class_="Attribute_attributeValue__lb_M5")
    Height = (height[8].text[:3])
    return Height
df_top200["Height"] = df_top200["URL"].apply(vasha_funkcia)
df_top200 = df_top200.sort_values(by=['Height'], ascending=True)

df["Overall by all stats"] = df["Passing"] + df["Dribbling"] + df["Pace"] + df["Defending"] + df["Shooting"] + df["Physicality"] + df["Sprint"] + df["Positioning"] + df["Finishing"] + df["Shot"] + df["Long"] + df["Volleys"] + df["Penalties"] + df["Vision"] + df["Crossing"] + df["Free"] + df["Curve"] + df["Agility"] + df["Balance"] + df["Reactions"] + df["Ball"] + df["Composure"] + df["Interceptions"] + df["Heading"] + df["Def"] + df["Standing"] + df["Sliding"] + df["Jumping"] + df["Stamina"] + df["Strength"] + df["Aggression"]
